Class SkipList<K,V>

java.lang.Object
SkipList<K,V>
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDictionary<K,V>
public class SkipList<K,V> extends Object implements IDictionary<K,V>
A simple skiplist implementation which realises a IDictionary interface. The skiplist stores key-values pairs with Integer keys and any comparable type for the value.
